1
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:21,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, will you keep 
teaching—no, I mean...</font>

2
00:00:21,710 --> 00:00:26,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, I humbly request that you 
continue teaching me to use a sword.</font>

3
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:28,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course.</font>

4
00:00:29,970 --> 00:00:32,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now that this guy's here, we'll be okay.</font>

5
00:00:32,730 --> 00:00:36,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I owe Shion-san my life, 
and he taught me to use a sword.</font>

6
00:00:36,010 --> 00:00:36,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow!</font>

7
00:00:36,850 --> 00:00:39,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not even these circumstances can stop 
you from acting like my teacher.</font>

8
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm actually kind of relieved.</font>

9
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:45,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You underestimate me.</font>

10
00:00:54,490 --> 00:00:56,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you, I'm used to that.</font>

11
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tenza!</font>

12
00:01:28,940 --> 00:01:31,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The one who takes cannot understand.</font>

13
00:01:32,740 --> 00:01:36,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But their victim never forgets.</font>

14
00:01:51,170 --> 00:01:52,090
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40"><font color="#2d1508">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

15
00:01:52,130 --> 00:01:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A faint flower was blooming 
unnoticed by anyone</i></font>

16
00:01:57,490 --> 00:02:02,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a burning red, 
but flickering serenely in red</i></font>

17
00:02:02,490 --> 00:02:07,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've been pausing for a long time 
dragging my past at my feet</i></font>

18
00:02:07,840 --> 00:02:10,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If I break free from this ambivalence,</i></font>

19
00:02:10,440 --> 00:02:13,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>will I be able to bloom by its side?</i></font>

20
00:02:13,850 --> 00:02:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The future is slipping away 
between my fingers</i></font>

21
00:02:16,490 --> 00:02:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What mistake did I make 
to pay this price?</i></font>

22
00:02:19,010 --> 00:02:23,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Always hurting myself</i></font>

23
00:02:23,860 --> 00:02:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and hesitant even to a small joy</i></font>

24
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:31,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to stop now</i></font>

25
00:02:31,410 --> 00:02:33,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The flower just bloomed in dignity</i></font>

26
00:02:33,930 --> 00:02:36,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and that was all I needed to be happy</i></font>

27
00:02:36,550 --> 00:02:41,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just wanted to protect this one flower</i></font>

28
00:02:41,670 --> 00:02:44,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wishing to be strong, I</i></font>

29
00:02:44,380 --> 00:02:47,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>picked up the vulnerability 
I had once cast away</i></font>

30
00:02:47,040 --> 00:02:48,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can't break free from the ambivalence</i></font>

31
00:02:48,990 --> 00:02:52,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In ambivalence, I become myself</i></font>

32
00:02:52,180 --> 00:02:54,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Like rooting strongly into the soil</i></font>

33
00:02:54,890 --> 00:02:57,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>like swaying ephemerally to the wind</i></font>

34
00:02:57,440 --> 00:03:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm slowly loosening myself to bloom</i></font>

35
00:03:00,530 --> 00:03:03,660
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="40">Hell's Paradise</font></b></font>

36
00:03:07,580 --> 00:03:12,500
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>Master and Student</b></font>

37
00:03:16,930 --> 00:03:19,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's exhausted their tao 
by continuously striking</i></font>

38
00:03:19,770 --> 00:03:21,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>the moment they start to regenerate.</i></font>

39
00:03:21,860 --> 00:03:25,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The wounds aren't fatal, but 
their regeneration has slowed a lot,</i></font>

40
00:03:25,540 --> 00:03:27,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and their appearance seems to be aging.</i></font>

41
00:03:28,190 --> 00:03:31,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They shouldn't be able to do much now.</i></font>

42
00:03:40,070 --> 00:03:44,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Inanimate objects can be controlled 
with the slightest amount of tao.</font>

43
00:03:44,980 --> 00:03:46,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die, human!</font>

44
00:04:00,580 --> 00:04:03,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll take this opportunity to recover.</i></font>

45
00:04:03,570 --> 00:04:06,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's exhausted as well.</i></font>

46
00:04:06,600 --> 00:04:11,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The repeated tao attacks 
are shortening his own life.</i></font>

47
00:04:15,480 --> 00:04:16,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

48
00:04:19,490 --> 00:04:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A childish trick. This is pointless.</font>

49
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tameshi Itto-ryu: Autumn Rains.</i></font>

50
00:04:37,100 --> 00:04:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He can't reach my tanden.</i></font>

51
00:04:40,420 --> 00:04:41,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Clink?</font>

52
00:04:55,150 --> 00:04:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're on the brink of death, too.</font>

53
00:04:59,530 --> 00:05:01,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with you?</font>

54
00:05:03,680 --> 00:05:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away!</font>

55
00:05:10,700 --> 00:05:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sen—</font>

56
00:05:29,010 --> 00:05:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong with you?</font>

57
00:05:31,320 --> 00:05:36,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd shorten your own life 
for someone who died?</font>

58
00:05:36,910 --> 00:05:38,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do all of this?</font>

59
00:05:42,810 --> 00:05:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't done anything yet.</font>

60
00:05:45,030 --> 00:05:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't mourn him or feel sadness yet.</font>

61
00:05:50,770 --> 00:05:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't even be angry 
while you're still alive.</font>

62
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:59,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it all once I've killed you.</font>

63
00:05:59,230 --> 00:06:01,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The despair and sadness 
can wait until after that.</font>

64
00:06:02,530 --> 00:06:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, how many more times 
do I have to cut you to kill you?</font>

65
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is bad. Really, really bad.</i></font>

66
00:06:10,990 --> 00:06:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have to do something.</i></font>

67
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:14,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Somehow...</i></font>

68
00:06:27,900 --> 00:06:29,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Don't panic.</i></font>

69
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tao doesn't recover quickly.</i></font>

70
00:06:42,510 --> 00:06:45,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you think you were close?</font>

71
00:06:45,210 --> 00:06:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't underestimate me, human.</font>

72
00:06:48,140 --> 00:06:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One of my kind was always 
both male and female,</font>

73
00:06:51,260 --> 00:06:55,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">circulating their energies 
by themselves to train.</font>

74
00:06:55,410 --> 00:06:57,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I copied that.</font>

75
00:06:58,080 --> 00:07:02,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's hard to maintain both sexes at once, 
but I have no choice now.</font>

76
00:07:02,900 --> 00:07:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides...</font>

77
00:07:06,060 --> 00:07:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I knew it. I thought that was the case.</font>

78
00:07:09,650 --> 00:07:11,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I can change part of myself,</font>

79
00:07:11,350 --> 00:07:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must be able to do the same 
with my transformation.</font>

80
00:07:16,200 --> 00:07:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, how many hundreds more 
times shall we continue?</font>

81
00:07:28,050 --> 00:07:31,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear I'll settle this.</font>

82
00:07:31,560 --> 00:07:35,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm used to your little stunts now.</font>

83
00:07:52,080 --> 00:07:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stunts.</i></font>

84
00:07:55,090 --> 00:07:56,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Call them what you want.</i></font>

85
00:07:56,540 --> 00:07:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is who I am.</i></font>

86
00:08:06,120 --> 00:08:09,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was scarred by my mother, 
a traveling entertainer.</i></font>

87
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:16,060
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#bea99b">See the Blade Master's Son</font></b></font>

88
00:08:12,300 --> 00:08:16,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Our act was a blind child dodging 
customer's strikes with a wooden sword.</i></font>

89
00:08:16,060 --> 00:08:19,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Behold the blade master's son 
who predicts attacks without seeing."</i></font>

90
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Both my mother and I were 
desperate to survive.</i></font>

91
00:08:25,330 --> 00:08:28,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The scars were part of the act, 
but I was born blind.</i></font>

92
00:08:28,950 --> 00:08:35,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As one who'd perceived the world 
through waves of tao, it was a simple act.</i></font>

93
00:08:38,180 --> 00:08:40,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A high-ranking kengyo heard about me</i></font>

94
00:08:40,030 --> 00:08:42,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and welcomed me into 
the Todoza guild for the blind.</i></font>

95
00:08:42,470 --> 00:08:45,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Through them, I knocked 
on the Yamada clan's doors.</i></font>

96
00:08:45,810 --> 00:08:50,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For a couple of poor entertainers, 
it was a golden opportunity.</i></font>

97
00:08:54,720 --> 00:08:59,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your child's skill with a sword 
makes it hard to believe he's blind.</font>

98
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where did he get those scars?</font>

99
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This boy's father is famed 
for his skill with a blade.</font>

100
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:09,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Blessed with talent, he was 
wounded in battle at a young age.</font>

101
00:09:09,640 --> 00:09:14,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Every time we were asked, 
my mother told the same lie.</i></font>

102
00:09:18,750 --> 00:09:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So did I.</i></font>

103
00:09:23,970 --> 00:09:29,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Unable to retract that explanation 
and ruin my mother's name,</i></font>

104
00:09:29,390 --> 00:09:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I spent my days as a Yamada 
student hiding my past.</i></font>

105
00:09:34,100 --> 00:09:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was ashamed.</i></font>

106
00:09:36,510 --> 00:09:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not like the past matters.</font>

107
00:09:39,050 --> 00:09:42,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's important is, 
you know, the present.</font>

108
00:09:43,520 --> 00:09:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not what I meant.</font>

109
00:09:45,130 --> 00:09:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I warned you to act 
like a Yamada student.</font>

110
00:09:47,630 --> 00:09:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am, and I wish you'd look at me, 
not my upbringing.</font>

111
00:09:54,580 --> 00:09:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tenza-kun and Shugen-san 
are fighting again.</font>

112
00:09:56,980 --> 00:09:58,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's amusing. Leave them be.</font>

113
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I envied Tenza's openness 
and fearlessness.</i></font>

114
00:10:06,520 --> 00:10:11,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As I saw others accept him 
for who he was, I felt potential.</i></font>

115
00:10:14,050 --> 00:10:18,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're incredible with a sword, sir.</font>

116
00:10:18,850 --> 00:10:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I look up to you.</font>

117
00:10:22,810 --> 00:10:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, I look up to you.</i></font>

118
00:10:34,870 --> 00:10:39,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I will kill you with my own hands, 
even if it costs me my life!</i></font>

119
00:10:50,130 --> 00:10:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can use my Kishikai form 
while recovering.</font>

120
00:10:53,360 --> 00:10:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You cannot win any—</font>

121
00:10:55,330 --> 00:10:56,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Silence.</font>

122
00:10:57,090 --> 00:11:01,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Both your appearance and 
flashy abilities are empty threats.</font>

123
00:11:01,680 --> 00:11:06,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're just focusing what little power 
you have left on putting on an act.</font>

124
00:11:06,480 --> 00:11:09,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soon, you'll have only 
as much tao as a human.</font>

125
00:11:09,780 --> 00:11:12,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your terrible acting can't fool me.</font>

126
00:11:13,160 --> 00:11:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither of us can strike a killing blow, 
so we'll drag each other through the mud.</font>

127
00:11:19,250 --> 00:11:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An ugly and deadly battle of endurance.</font>

128
00:11:22,610 --> 00:11:23,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you ready?</font>

129
00:11:28,000 --> 00:11:29,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

130
00:11:30,730 --> 00:11:31,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nurugai.</font>

131
00:11:36,660 --> 00:11:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay back. I'll handle the rest.</font>

132
00:11:40,860 --> 00:11:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

133
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's about to get dangerous.</font>

134
00:11:48,900 --> 00:11:50,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn you!</font>

135
00:11:59,610 --> 00:12:03,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With no ability to hinder them, 
I can only hope to exhaust them.</i></font>

136
00:12:03,280 --> 00:12:07,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So how can I expend 
my own tao efficiently?</i></font>

137
00:12:08,150 --> 00:12:10,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't have to cut 
them hundreds of times.</font>

138
00:12:10,670 --> 00:12:13,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wouldn't it be easier 
to skewer them with your sword?</font>

139
00:12:13,690 --> 00:12:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True.</font>

140
00:12:15,350 --> 00:12:17,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That should be physically possible.</font>

141
00:12:17,450 --> 00:12:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Tensen's tanden seem to be 
ovules within their bodies.</font>

142
00:12:22,190 --> 00:12:25,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Skewering would be efficient 
for exhausting their tao</font>

143
00:12:25,160 --> 00:12:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">through continuous regeneration.</font>

144
00:12:30,910 --> 00:12:34,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sever their limbs, or perhaps...</font>

145
00:12:36,170 --> 00:12:39,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">extract only the ovule and skewer it.</font>

146
00:12:39,890 --> 00:12:43,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we're familiar with the practice 
of Hiemontori, it should be easy.</font>

147
00:12:44,300 --> 00:12:47,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The question is whether 
you can keep them skewered.</font>

148
00:12:47,220 --> 00:12:48,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right.</font>

149
00:12:48,790 --> 00:12:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just imagining it grosses me out. 
I could never.</font>

150
00:13:02,800 --> 00:13:05,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regenerate. Vines grow.</font>

151
00:13:05,680 --> 00:13:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pull sword out.</font>

152
00:13:07,450 --> 00:13:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stop you even if you hold in place.</font>

153
00:13:10,890 --> 00:13:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Enter you.</font>

154
00:13:12,940 --> 00:13:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

155
00:13:18,590 --> 00:13:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're weaker than I imagined.</i></font>

156
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it because I exhausted their tao?</i></font>

157
00:13:24,060 --> 00:13:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I told you it'd be a battle of endurance.</font>

158
00:13:28,330 --> 00:13:32,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who will exhaust themselves first, 
you or me?</font>

159
00:13:32,340 --> 00:13:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm here to settle the score.</font>

160
00:13:35,790 --> 00:13:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we both die, then I win!</font>

161
00:13:39,080 --> 00:13:43,050
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b><font color="#040004"><font size="40">Hell's Paradise</font></font></b></font>

162
00:13:52,530 --> 00:13:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This pain is nothing compared 
to his final moments...</i></font>

163
00:13:58,390 --> 00:14:00,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei, stop!</font>

164
00:14:00,570 --> 00:14:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you keep going, you'll die!</font>

165
00:14:02,820 --> 00:14:03,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay away!</font>

166
00:14:05,510 --> 00:14:09,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I keep fighting, I can take 
the monster down with me.</font>

167
00:14:09,700 --> 00:14:14,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should get out of here 
and find the others.</font>

168
00:14:15,320 --> 00:14:18,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will remain here.</font>

169
00:14:19,920 --> 00:14:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't make sense.</font>

170
00:14:23,370 --> 00:14:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're smart.</font>

171
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:28,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You think things through.</font>

172
00:14:28,220 --> 00:14:31,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know how to make the right choice.</font>

173
00:14:31,730 --> 00:14:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't like you!</font>

174
00:14:36,830 --> 00:14:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that moment, I instantly 
understood his scream.</font>

175
00:14:43,460 --> 00:14:45,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He knew we couldn't win 
and wanted some of us to survive.</font>

176
00:14:45,810 --> 00:14:49,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understood his intentions 
and acted instantly.</font>

177
00:14:50,370 --> 00:14:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was the right choice.</font>

178
00:14:54,590 --> 00:14:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why did I have to make the right choice?</font>

179
00:14:59,700 --> 00:15:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it was foolish, 
why couldn't I have gone to him?</font>

180
00:15:04,750 --> 00:15:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He must've spent his final moments 
drowning in regret and pain.</font>

181
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:15,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And all I could do was run. 
I can't forgive myself.</font>

182
00:15:17,970 --> 00:15:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even while losing someone I loved, 
I made the right choice.</font>

183
00:15:23,830 --> 00:15:25,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't forgive myself.</font>

184
00:15:27,990 --> 00:15:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These eyes can't even shed tears, 
so at the very least...</font>

185
00:15:37,170 --> 00:15:38,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sensei!</font>

186
00:15:39,690 --> 00:15:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me handle this and go to the others.</font>

187
00:15:43,970 --> 00:15:46,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... that's not...</font>

188
00:15:46,170 --> 00:15:47,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

189
00:15:47,930 --> 00:15:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry!</font>

190
00:16:00,570 --> 00:16:04,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's like I was back then.</i></font>

191
00:16:05,310 --> 00:16:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I lost the people I loved 
and couldn't forgive myself.</i></font>

192
00:16:16,490 --> 00:16:21,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He doesn't know if he 
should live or die, like me.</i></font>

193
00:16:22,790 --> 00:16:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the sole survivor. 
Everyone else died because of me.</font>

194
00:16:34,060 --> 00:16:36,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get it.</font>

195
00:16:38,810 --> 00:16:41,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm asking if you want to die.</font>

196
00:16:43,350 --> 00:16:46,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, that's right.</font>

197
00:16:46,990 --> 00:16:49,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until you explain it to me...</font>

198
00:16:50,230 --> 00:16:56,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until I understand it, I... I'm not...</font>

199
00:17:06,340 --> 00:17:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ten... Tenza...</font>

200
00:17:09,370 --> 00:17:16,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I, um... um, Sensei is... I...</font>

201
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:25,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then there's only one thing to do.</font>

202
00:17:29,440 --> 00:17:30,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

203
00:17:42,630 --> 00:17:45,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until you explain it to me...</font>

204
00:17:45,140 --> 00:17:49,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Until I understand it, I'm not leaving.</font>

205
00:17:52,800 --> 00:17:55,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't hear anything anymore.</i></font>

206
00:17:56,740 --> 00:18:01,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't know how much time has passed 
or how much more I can take.</i></font>

207
00:18:02,690 --> 00:18:09,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The only thing I can feel is my life 
slowly and clearly being eaten away.</i></font>

208
00:18:16,530 --> 00:18:22,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Slowly means skewering them 
was effective.</i></font>

209
00:18:24,220 --> 00:18:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tenza, finally...</i></font>

210
00:18:36,290 --> 00:18:37,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nuru...</font>

211
00:18:53,420 --> 00:18:54,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing?</font>

212
00:18:54,700 --> 00:18:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holding you so your tao will recover.</font>

213
00:18:58,790 --> 00:19:01,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This isn't the time.</font>

214
00:19:03,090 --> 00:19:06,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Girls should be more cautious 
about who they hold.</font>

215
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You shouldn't be doing that 
for all kinds of reasons.</font>

216
00:19:11,150 --> 00:19:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you're starting 
to sound like yourself.</font>

217
00:19:16,150 --> 00:19:17,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look.</font>

218
00:19:18,350 --> 00:19:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're not dead, 
but their regeneration has slowed.</font>

219
00:19:21,980 --> 00:19:24,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll take a day for them to recover.</font>

220
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:28,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So we should kill them now.</font>

221
00:19:28,100 --> 00:19:31,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, so we should leave it be.</font>

222
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:34,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'll stab you with vines 
if you get close again.</font>

223
00:19:34,980 --> 00:19:37,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you keep going, you'll die.</font>

224
00:19:37,970 --> 00:19:40,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go join the others.</font>

225
00:19:44,700 --> 00:19:46,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't do that.</font>

226
00:19:47,850 --> 00:19:51,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tenza won't be avenged 
until they stop breathing.</font>

227
00:19:52,250 --> 00:19:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His suffering...</font>

228
00:19:55,630 --> 00:19:56,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're wrong.</font>

229
00:19:58,310 --> 00:20:01,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't suffer or die with regrets.</font>

230
00:20:02,070 --> 00:20:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm wrong?</font>

231
00:20:04,240 --> 00:20:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you carried me away, I saw him.</font>

232
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:12,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He smiled.</font>

233
00:20:13,250 --> 00:20:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He saw us running away and smiled.</font>

234
00:20:16,740 --> 00:20:20,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've been suffering 
because you didn't know that.</font>

235
00:20:21,170 --> 00:20:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's because you had to 
carry me. I'm sorry.</font>

236
00:20:25,010 --> 00:20:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was a nice smile.</font>

237
00:20:27,570 --> 00:20:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sad but cool.</font>

238
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you don't have to avenge him, Sensei.</font>

239
00:20:44,090 --> 00:20:50,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We haven't talked much about Tenza 
because we've been focused on revenge.</font>

240
00:20:51,740 --> 00:20:56,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me. I want to know more about him.</font>

241
00:20:57,270 --> 00:21:02,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should talk more 
once we leave this place alive.</font>

242
00:21:25,060 --> 00:21:26,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're right.</font>

243
00:21:26,870 --> 00:21:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's end this. 
I won't take this too far.</font>

244
00:21:33,270 --> 00:21:35,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's join the others.</font>

245
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:38,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

246
00:21:39,990 --> 00:21:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Nurugai.</font>

247
00:21:42,900 --> 00:21:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've given me life.</font>

248
00:21:54,010 --> 00:21:57,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should be calling you sensei.</font>

249
00:21:57,650 --> 00:21:59,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You opened my eyes.</font>

250
00:22:00,430 --> 00:22:01,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can't hear me, can you?</font>

251
00:22:10,140 --> 00:22:13,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They got Zhu Jin.</font>

252
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:16,770
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an9}<font color="#811a1a">Shion</font></b></font>

253
00:22:13,770 --> 00:22:16,770
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}<font color="#811a1a">Nurugai</font></b></font>

254
00:22:17,600 --> 00:22:19,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shion-dono...</font>

255
00:22:19,530 --> 00:22:21,530
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#811a1a">Shion</font></b></font>

256
00:22:23,330 --> 00:22:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Won't you reconsider?</font>

257
00:22:26,060 --> 00:22:30,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll both just keep 
losing people we care about.</font>

258
00:22:30,410 --> 00:22:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's too sad to continue.</font>

259
00:22:35,580 --> 00:22:36,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please.</font>

260
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:46,550
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#9d2e21"><font size="8">Yuzuriha</font></font></b></font>

261
00:22:44,050 --> 00:22:46,550
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#9f3221"><font size="8">Gabimaru</font></font></b></font>

262
00:22:46,550 --> 00:22:49,560
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#9f3221">Gabimaru</font></b></font>

263
00:22:50,560 --> 00:22:55,060
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#9f3221">Gabimaru</font></b></font>

264
00:23:08,100 --> 00:23:14,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>On the other side, even today</i></font>

265
00:23:14,230 --> 00:23:20,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Someone is unraveling, 
yet they still stand</i></font>

266
00:23:20,190 --> 00:23:26,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A stab to the chest, this loneliness</i></font>

267
00:23:26,100 --> 00:23:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Points and lines, 
breaking off and vanishing</i></font>

268
00:23:31,930 --> 00:23:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My shattered mask</i></font>

269
00:23:34,830 --> 00:23:37,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's more than I can bear</i></font>

270
00:23:37,910 --> 00:23:40,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I must keep on living</i></font>

271
00:23:40,900 --> 00:23:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Tomorrow awaits to greet me</i></font>

272
00:23:45,690 --> 00:23:48,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's endless</i></font>

273
00:23:48,650 --> 00:23:51,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And so fragile</i></font>

274
00:23:51,220 --> 00:23:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is it better to believe 
hearts don't exist at all?</i></font>

275
00:23:57,450 --> 00:24:03,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Radiant and soft</i></font>

276
00:24:03,010 --> 00:24:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Was the hand</i></font>

277
00:24:04,720 --> 00:24:13,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I squeezed back on that day</i></font>

